
The Letter ni filime documentaire ifite iminota 84 yo muri Kenya 2019 iyobowe na maia Lekow  afatanyije na Christopher King<ref>https://www.filmafrica.org/film-africa-2020/the-letter-uk-online/</ref><ref>https://screenworlds.org/resources/the-letter-2019-director-qa-with-film-africa/</ref>. Yatoranijwe nkumunyakenya winjiye muri Filime Nziza Mpuzamahanga Yamamaye muri 93 Awards Academy, ariko ntabwo yatowe<ref>https://screenworlds.org/resources/the-letter-2019-director-qa-with-film-africa/</ref>. 

== Inyandiko ==
Umusore yasuye umudugudu wa nyirakuru kugira ngo amenye ko yashinjwaga kuroga.<ref>https://variety.com/2019/film/festivals/idfa-the-letter-trailer-1203406004/</ref><ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_fiche_film/59746_1</ref> 

